## Harness usage

```text
/plan         → Plans.md from requirements (planner subagent, opus)
/work N       → implement Phase N (coder + tester subagents)
/review       → 4-lens gate (reviewer subagent, opus)
/release      → 🔒 PR + docs (must type manually)
/setup        → bootstrap a new subproject
/orchestrator → full loop with checkpoints (experimental, ~5x cost)
```

## Subagents

`@agent-explorer @agent-planner @agent-coder @agent-tester @agent-reviewer @agent-documenter`

- planner / reviewer: opus (expensive decisions)
- explorer / coder / tester / documenter: sonnet (execution)

